pwiz::msdata::OBO

pwiz::msdata::OBO Struct Reference

#include <obo.hpp>

List of all members.

Detailed Description

Represents a selectively parsed OBO file.

Note that the following are currently ignored during parsing:

  • comments
  • dbxrefs
  • synonym tags other than exact_synonym
  • non-Term stanzas
  • obsolete Terms
